<i>♪ Playing in the limits ♪</i>

39:50.246 --> 39:51.378
<i>♪ It's a fragile world ♪</i>

39:51.413 --> 39:52.579
<i>♪ Fragile world ♪</i>

39:52.615 --> 39:53.615
<i>♪ Fragile world ♪</i>

39:53.649 --> 39:55.449
<i>♪ Playing in the limits ♪</i>

39:55.484 --> 39:57.551
<i>♪ Catching fire
under the stars ♪</i>

39:57.586 --> 39:59.586
<i>♪ I'm ready to feel ♪</i>

39:59.622 --> 40:01.588
<i>♪ The uneasy pain... ♪</i>

40:01.624 --> 40:03.590
I'm not saying thank you.

40:03.626 --> 40:07.494
<i>♪ Oh the burden that I face... ♪</i>

40:07.530 --> 40:09.363
<i>♪ Inside, every night ♪</i>

40:09.398 --> 40:10.564
Magnus, you were right.

40:10.633 --> 40:12.399
<i>♪ I'm a stranger when I wake ♪</i>

40:12.434 --> 40:14.234
<i>♪ Wake up in your eyes ♪</i>

40:14.270 --> 40:15.480
You never have to
prove yourself to me.

40:15.504 --> 40:17.404
<i>♪</i>

40:17.439 --> 40:19.439
I love you.

40:23.679 --> 40:27.281
I love you, too.

40:27.316 --> 40:31.418
<i>♪ Forever alone... ♪</i>

40:31.453 --> 40:32.586
<i>♪</i>

40:32.621 --> 40:33.520
JACE: Maia...

40:33.556 --> 40:34.521
<i>♪</i>

40:34.557 --> 40:36.423
Look, I'm sorry if I hurt you.

40:36.458 --> 40:37.558
If?

40:37.593 --> 40:40.561
You were willing to let the
entire Downworld go to hell

40:40.596 --> 40:42.229
because you're still
in love with Clary.

40:42.264 --> 40:43.397
I'm not in love with Clary.

40:43.432 --> 40:43.730
Please.

40:43.766 --> 40:44.631
I'm not.

40:44.667 --> 40:46.633
Prove it.

40:46.669 --> 40:49.369
<i>♪ I'm hiding away ♪</i>

40:49.405 --> 40:51.538
<i>♪</i>

40:55.244 --> 40:56.521
And don't think
this means anything.

